            <title><![CDATA[Dead Take launches July 31]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/dead-take-launches-july-31</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/dead-take-launches-july-31.1244931/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Full cast of psychological horror game announced.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Psychological <a title="Genres > Horror [660 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/horror">horror game</a> <em><a title="Games > Dead Take [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dead-take">Dead Take</a></em> will launch for <a title="Platforms > PC [23,676 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3352690/Dead_Take/" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a title="Companies > Epic Games [352 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/epic-games">Epic Games</a> Store on July 31, <a title="Companies > Pocketpair Publishing [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/pocketpair/pocketpair-publishing">Pocketpair Publishing</a> developer <a title="Companies > Surgent Studios [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/surgent-studios">Surgent Studios</a> announced. <span id="more-978861"></span></p><p>“Dead Take is about actors,” said <em>Dead Take</em> creative director Abubakar Salim in a press release. “So we needed actors who’ve lived it. It’s a game about the high of ambition and the rot underneath it. The lies we tell ourselves to get in the spotlight, and the monsters we become to stay there. Everyone in this cast has felt that pressure. This was a chance to bleed it out.”</p><p>Here are the latest details, via Pocketpair Publishing:</p><blockquote><p>Alongside the release date, the full lineup of cast members were announced including Jane Perry (<em><a title="Games > Baldur's Gate III [27 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii">Baldur’s Gate III</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Dragon Age: The Veilguard [18 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragon-age-the-veilguard">Dragon Age: The Veilguard</a></em>), and Alanah Pearce (<em><a title="Games > Cyberpunk 2077 [72 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/cyberpunk-2077">Cyberpunk 2077</a></em>, <em>V/H/S/Beyond</em>). <em>Dead Take</em>‘s cast also includes cameo appearances from Laura Bailey (<em>The Last of Us: Part II</em>, <em><a title="Games > Marvel's Spider-Man 2 [24 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/marvels-spider-man-2">Marvel’s Spider-Man 2</a></em>), Matthew Mercer (<em>Critical Role</em>, <em><a title="Games > Final Fantasy VII [69 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/final-fantasy-vii">Final Fantasy VII</a>: Rebirth</em>), Sam <a title="Games > Lake [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/lake">Lake</a> (<em><a title="Games > Alan Wake II [20 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/alan-wake-ii">Alan Wake II</a></em>, <em>Max Payne</em>), Travis Willingham (<em><a title="Games > Marvel Rivals [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/marvel-rivals">Marvel Rivals</a></em>, <em>Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order</em>), and CDawgVA (<em><a title="Games > Honkai: Star Rail [40 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/honkai-star-rail">Honkai: Star Rail</a></em>, <em>Card-En-Ciel</em>).</p><p>Set in a luxurious yet secluded Hollywood Hills mansion, Dead Take casts players as an actor (Neil Newbon as Chase Lowry) searching for his friend (Ben Starr as Vinny Monroe) gone missing after a lavish Hollywood party. As they navigate escape-room-style puzzles and splice together videos they find along the way, players will uncover the darkest secrets behind the entertainment industry’s glittering facade.</p></blockquote><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <h2><span>Release Date Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="DEAD TAKE | FULL CAST REVEALED | OFFICIAL TRAILER" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aXhJB9ICvfc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/dead-take-launches-july-31]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
