            <title><![CDATA[KAKU: Ancient Seal for PS5, Xbox Series launches in late 2025]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/kaku-ancient-seal-for-ps5-xbox-series-launches-in-late-2025</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/kaku-ancient-seal-for-ps5-xbox-series-launches-in-late-2025.1244925/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Currently available for PC.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Open-world <a title="Genres > Action [2,872 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a> <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,400 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure game</a> <em><a title="Games > KAKU: Ancient Seal [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/kaku-ancient-seal">KAKU: Ancient Seal</a></em> will launch for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,903 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,526 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a> in late 2025, developer <a title="Companies > BINGOBELL [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bingobell">BINGOBELL</a> announced. A physical edition distributed by <a title="Companies > Microids [207 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/microids">Microids</a> will also be available for PlayStation 5. The console versions were ported by <a title="Companies > SneakyBox [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sneakybox">SneakyBox</a>. <span id="more-978771"></span></p><p><em>KAKU: Ancient Seal</em> first launched in Early Access for PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179580/KAKU_Ancient_Seal/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on May 3, 2023, followed by a full release on July 12, 2024.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via its <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179580/KAKU_Ancient_Seal/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam page</a>:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>An <a title="Genres > Open-World [677 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/open-world">open-world</a> action adventure combining exploration with puzzles and dynamic combat. Go on a journey across a sprawling continent as Kaku, a young boy tasked to restore balance to the land. Brave the four elemental regions with the help of Piggy, his powerful companion and conquer their lords.</p><p><strong>Story</strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><em>KAKU: Ancient Seal</em> is an open-world <a title="Genres > Action RPG [1,715 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/action-rpg">action RPG</a> with an ancient fantasy theme. Set in a primordial era, this world was created by the elemental power of the Creator Saga. One day, a calamity from another realm strikes, causing the dispersion of the elemental souls, and the world splits into four continents, while the Creator Saga goes missing.</p><p><a title="Games > Millennia [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/millennia">Millennia</a> later, a young man named Kaku, living in the vast snowy mountains, along with Piggy, a flying pig, shoulders the task of finding the lost elemental souls under the guidance of a lost prophecy. They embark on an ancient and fantastical adventure to uncover the truth behind the calamity and the mystery of their own origins.</p><p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Craft Your Unique Combat Style</strong><ul><li>Unleash exciting combos and execute moves effortlessly.</li><li>Tailor your combat style by exploring diverse skill branches to create your own style.</li><li>Equip an array of equipment and pair them with Rune Stones for endless gameplay possibilities, and fun experiences.</li><li><a title="Companies > Mas [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/mas">Mas</a>ter elemental pellets, strategically employing their effects to defeat enemies.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Unlock Divine Power: Incarnate the Creator Saga and <a title="Companies > Experience [212 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/experience">Experience</a> Musou Battles</strong><ul><li>Embrace your role as the chosen one and and harness the lost diviner power of the Creator Saga.</li><li>Experience the thrill of transformation, embodying the incarnation of the Creator Sage in battle.</li><li>Engage in epic encounters and unleash the power of Musou, immersion yourself in unparalleled combat experiences.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Experience the Challenges and Puzzles in the World of Ruins</strong><ul><li>Delve into the void left by the Creator Saga, where ancient ruins beckon with their unique designs and challenges.</li><li>Solve diverse puzzles and encounter obstacles in each ruin, ensuring a fresh and engaging experience in each of them.</li><li>Use your courage and wit to navigate through the World of Ruins, overcoming obstacles to claim valuable rewards.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Embark on an Epic Journey Through a Vast <a title="Companies > Ancient [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/ancient">Ancient</a> Fantasy World</strong><ul><li>Explore diverse elemental continents with Piggy, from the icy expanses of the <a title="Games > Howl [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/howl">Howl</a>ing Snowfield to the murky depths of the Misty Swamps, uncovering stories and secrets lurking behind every adventure.</li><li>Deal with the continent’s indigenous inhabitants, the Ponpon and uncover hidden tales by completing various marvellous events.</li><li>Master the abilities of your flying pig companion, fostering a bond that leads to a joyful and humorous journey together.</li><li>Explore the untamed wilderness, ancient ruins, and mysterious caves in pursuit of long-forgotten treasures.</li></ul></li></ul></blockquote><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>Consoles Release Window Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="KAKU: Ancient Seal – ESRB Console Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JDTIx5r8Ba8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/kaku-ancient-seal-for-ps5-xbox-series-launches-in-late-2025]]></content:encoded>
